:

*Mislimo* da će doći ranije. (We think that they are going to come earlier.)
*Mislimo* li da će biti bolje? (Do we think that it will be better?)
Vi *mislimo* da će to biti moguće. (We think that it will be possible.)
*Mislimo* li da je to prava stvar? (Do we think that this is the right thing?)
*Mislimo* li da je to dobar izbor? (Do we think that this is a good choice?)